	(text_box "sf = 5\nI_{L, avg} = ((5V - (-12V)) / (0.8 * 5V)) * 30mA * sf\nI_{L, avg} = 638mA\n\nChoose ripple current to be max 20% of average inductor current\nDelta(I) = 128mA\n\nL = (5V * -12V)/(128mA * (-12V - 5V) * 1.38MHz)\nL = 2.0uH"
